Time":"2017-03-14T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>先沖水<br />\n後抺一次<br />\n再用消毒抹一次<br />\n再抺乾<br />\n再鋪紙巾<br />\n<br />\n用完個啲紙就掉入去壓水花<br />\n<br />\n舒舒服服坐半個鐘</blockquote><br />\n想知女人去小便有幾多個會咁乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小便洗鬼搞咁多野 扎個馬 連廁板都唔會掂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96106361a9fd5da4273279c39f228c6f38885d1e","tid":154422,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:51:32.000Z","msg":"其實扎馬去廁所係咪男人先會<br />\n好似無乜聽女人會扎馬去"},{"pid":"b26cc14f0b437525b7b429a692370a8f9cfd694b","tid":154422,"uid":77724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T01:35:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>先沖水<br />\n後抺一次<br />\n再用消毒抹一次<br />\n再抺乾<br />\n再鋪紙巾<br />\n<br />\n用完個啲紙就掉入去壓水花<br />\n<br />\n舒舒服服坐半個鐘</blockquote><br />\n想知女人去小便有幾多個會咁乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個廁板應該幾乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係&quot;乾淨&quot;到痺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小便就9成札馬嫁喇，<br />\n但個撚個唔拉起廁板就痾，<br />\n搞到公廁廁板10 次有9次都見到有尿積係上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我覺得男廁一定乾淨過女廁，聽人講係痾屎先會去馬桶。<br />\n消毒液我就唔用嘅（用過一兩次覺得超級麻煩），<br />\n係公司就咁鋪紙巾就去，<br />\n街外公廁就極少痾屎，幾年前試過抹乾之後鋪紙巾就去。"},{"pid":"cc652d443e2328fe09c54f479cafe29c4b438912","tid":154422,"uid":77724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T01:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>先沖水<br />\n後抺一次<br />\n再用消毒抹一次<br />\n再抺乾<br />\n再鋪紙巾<br />\n<br />\n用完個啲紙就掉入去壓水花<br />\n<br />\n舒舒服服坐半個鐘</blockquote><br />\n想知女人去小便有幾多個會咁乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個廁板應該幾乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係&quot;乾淨&quot;到痺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小便就9成<span style=\"color: red;\">扎</span>馬嫁喇，<br />\n但個撚個唔拉起廁板就痾，<br />\n搞到公廁廁板10 次有9次都見到有尿積係上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我覺得男廁一定乾淨過女廁，聽人講係痾屎先會去馬桶。<br />\n消毒液我就唔用嘅（用過一兩次覺得超級麻煩），<br />\n係公司就咁鋪紙巾就去，<br />\n街外公廁就極少痾屎，幾年前試過抹乾之後鋪紙巾就去。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8739bbdafc779b1c767e31ba497dbcddd34db96c","tid":154422,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T01:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>先沖水<br />\n後抺一次<br />\n再用消毒抹一次<br />\n再抺乾<br />\n再鋪紙巾<br />\n<br />\n用完個啲紙就掉入去壓水花<br />\n<br />\n舒舒服服坐半個鐘</blockquote><br />\n想知女人去小便有幾多個會咁乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個廁板應該幾乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係&quot;乾淨&quot;到痺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小便就9成<span style=\"color: red;\">扎</span>馬嫁喇，<br />\n但個撚個唔拉起廁板就痾，<br />\n搞到公廁廁板10 次有9次都見到有尿積係上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我覺得男廁一定乾淨過女廁，聽人講係痾屎先會去馬桶。<br />\n消毒液我就唔用嘅（用過一兩次覺得超級麻煩），<br />\n係公司就咁鋪紙巾就去，<br />\n街外公廁就極少痾屎，幾年前試過抹乾之後鋪紙巾就去。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bbb64b88b7d05e35224c30806f6b721cf66d5b","tid":154422,"uid":73677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T01:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>先沖水<br />\n後抺一次<br />\n再用消毒抹一次<br />\n再抺乾<br />\n再鋪紙巾<br />\n<br />\n用完個啲紙就掉入去壓水花<br />\n<br />\n舒舒服服坐半個鐘</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打痾完紙巾抹完，再